-- Solar Millennium Cuts Sales Forecast, Says May Post Ebit Loss This Year
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-10-13T06:10:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/solar-millennium-cuts-sales-forecast-says-may-post-ebit-loss-this-year.html
Solar Millennium AG reduced its
sales forecast for the current fiscal year to 150 million euros
from 350 million euros, and its earnings before interest and
taxes forecast to a “neutral or slightly negative Ebit.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Gavin at 
